---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import VideoGrid from '../components/VideoGrid.jsx';
---

<Layout title="Start Here - Toby Glenn">
 <main class="min-h-screen bg-neutral-950 text-white">
 {/* Hero Section */}
 <section class="pt-32 pb-16 md:pt-40 md:pb-24 relative overflow-hidden">
 <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-900/10 to-transparent pointer-events-none" />
 <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
 <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-12 items-start">
 <div class="lg:w-2/3">
 <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-blue-600/20 border border-blue-500/30 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-blue-400 text-sm font-semibold mb-6">
 ðŸ‘‹ New here?
 </span>
 <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight">
 Serious fitness,<br />
 <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-purple-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent">real results, zero hype</span>
 </h1>
 <p class="text-xl text-neutral-400 mb-8 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
 I'm Toby Glenn. I dropped from 242 lbs to 188 lbs in 6 months while training with a broken ankle. 
 I don't sell products or lifestyle aesthetics â€” I document what actually works, with real numbers.
 </p>
 <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
 <a href="#recommended" class="px-8 py-4 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold rounded-full transition-all hover:scale-105 text-center">
 Watch My First 3 Videos
 </a>
 <a href="/videos" class="px-8 py-4 bg-neutral-900 hover:bg-neutral-800 text-white border border-neutral-800 rounded-full transition-all font-medium text-center">
 Browse All Videos
 </a>
 </div>
 </div>
 
 {/* Stats Card */}
 <div class="lg:w-1/3 bg-neutral-900 border border-neutral-800 rounded-2xl p-8">
 <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-6 text-blue-400">The Numbers</h2>
 <div className="space-y-4">
 <div class="border-b border-neutral-800 pb-4">
 <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">242 â†’ 188</div>
 <div class="text-sm text-neutral-400">lbs dropped in 6 months</div>
 </div>
 <div class="border-b border-neutral-800 pb-4">
 <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">600K+</div>
 <div class="text-sm text-neutral-400">pounds lifted on Speediance</div>
 </div>
 <div class="border-b border-neutral-800 pb-4">
 <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">41,500</div>
 <div class="text-sm text-neutral-400">lbs per workout</div>
 </div>
 <div>
 <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">100+</div>
 <div class="text-sm text-neutral-400">videos documenting the journey</div>
 </div>
 </div>
 </div>
 </div>
 </div>
 </section>

 {/* Who I Am */}
 <section class="py-16 border-t border-neutral-900">
 <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
 <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Who is Toby Glenn?</h2>
 <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed">
 <div class="space-y-4">
 <p>
 I'm not a coach who talks from a distance. I'm in the lab every day â€” testing wearables, 
 equipment, and training methods so you don't have to waste time on what doesn't work.
 </p>
 <p>
 My content spans six pillars: <strong>Speediance Authority</strong> (I've become the definitive 
 independent resource), <strong>BJJ & Grappling Insight</strong> (thoughtful commentary on culture 
 and match analysis), <strong>Transformation</strong> (my documented 242â†’188 lb journey), 
 <strong>Tech Reviews</strong> (Whoop, Garmin, and wearables), <strong>Training Methodology</strong> 
 (real splits and volume), and <strong>AI/Productivity</strong> (OpenClaw, BJJ Buddy).
 </p>
 </div>
 <div class="space-y-4">
 <p>
 What makes this different? I bring an engineer's mentality: test it, measure it, call out what's 
 broken, and share what actually works. No sponsorships influencing opinions. No hype.
 </p>
 <p>
 The throughline: <em>no-BS fitness for serious adults who don't have time for nonsense.</em>
 Whether you're deciding between Tonal and Speediance, navigating BJJ belt culture, or trying 
 to get back in shape, I give you signal, not noise.
 </p>
 </div>
 </div>
 </div>
 </section>

 {/* Content Pillars */}
 <section class="py-16 bg-neutral-900/30 border-y border-neutral-900">
 <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
 <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">Content Pillars</h2>
 <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
 {[
 { name: 'Speediance Authority', desc: 'Firmware deep dives, mode comparisons, real-world testing' },
 { name: 'BJJ Insight', desc: 'Match analysis, belt culture, informed commentary' },
 { name: 'Transformation', desc: 'Documented weight loss, setbacks, honest progress' },
 { name: 'Tech Reviews', desc: 'Wearables, trackers, whoop vs garmin' },
 { name: 'Methodology', desc: 'Training splits, volume, progressive overload' },
 { name: 'AI/Productivity', desc: 'OpenClaw setup, BJJ Buddy, automation' }
 ].map(pillar => (
 <div class="bg-neutral-900 border border-neutral-800 rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-blue-500/50 transition-colors">
 <h3 class="font-bold text-white mb-2">{pillar.name}</h3>
 <p class="text-sm text-neutral-400">{pillar.desc}</p>
 </div>
 ))}
 </div>
 </div>
 </section>

 {/* Recommended Videos */}
 <section id="recommended" class="py-16">
 <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
 <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-8">
 <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold">Start With These</h2>
 <span class="text-neutral-500">Three pillars, three entry points</span>
 </div>
 <VideoGrid client:load limit={3} showFilters={false} />
 </div>
 </section>

 {/* Newsletter CTA */}
 <section class="py-16 border-t border-neutral-900">
 <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
 <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Join the Newsletter</h2>
 <p class="text-neutral-400 mb-8 max-w-xl mx-auto">
 New videos, honest reviews, and real training data â€” delivered when it matters, not when the algorithm decides.
 </p>
 <form class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center max-w-md mx-auto">
 <input 
 type="email" 
 placeholder="your@email.com" 
 class="flex-1 bg-neutral-900 border border-neutral-800 rounded-full px-6 py-3 text-white focus:border-blue-500 outline-none"
 />
 <button type="submit" class="px-8 py-3 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold rounded-full transition-colors">
 Subscribe
 </button>
 </form>
 <p class="text-xs text-neutral-600 mt-4">No spam. Unsubscribe anytime.</p>
 </div>
 </section>
 </main>
</Layout>
